2.write a program which prints a statement as- " Hello, i am(vishvas)."
on the output screen.?
=Ans:

#include<stdio.h>
#include<conio.h>
void main()
{
    printf("\n Hello, i am ( vishvas vaja)");
    
    getch();
}


